   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>"Year fourteen of Imperator Caesar Trajanus Hadrianus Augustus [Month, Day]. Paid through the praktor Aquilla by Heraklous alias Thena[], freedwoman of D[] for the naubion katoikonof the 14th year for Kerkeesis 400 (+ ?)bronze dr(achmas), for additional charges 40(+ ?) (bronze drachmas), for exchange 10(+ ?) (bronze drachmas), for receipt 1 ob(ol) and 1/2 ob(ol)."</ab>
         </div>
